# sphinx-imgur

Embed [Imgur](https://imgur.com) images and albums in Sphinx documents/pages.

* Python 3.6, 3.7, 3.8, and 3.9 supported on Linux, macOS, and Windows.

ðŸ“– Full documentation: https://sphinx-imgur.readthedocs.io

