## Quickstart

To install run the following:

```bash
pip install sphinx-imgur
```

To use in Sphinx simply add to your `conf.py`:

```python
extensions = ["sphinx_imgur.imgur"]
```

And in your Sphinx documents:

```rst
.. imgur:: 611EovQ
```

Or to use Imgur's embed feature with an album:

```rst
.. imgur-embed:: a/9YZHA
```

